#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:2
msgid "快速开始"
msgstr "Quick Start"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:4
msgid ""
"PCBA AOI 软件是一款面向电子制造的智能光学检测系统。 系统以视觉 AI 为核心，提供从自动建模、参数生成到缺陷检测与持续优化的完整流程。 "
"与传统需要频繁手动调参的方式不同，系统可快速适配生产现场，在提升效率的同时确保精度与稳定性。 "
"依托自适应算法与反馈机制，软件既能识别常见与细微缺陷，也能在生产过程中持续学习，提升良率并降低运维成本。"
msgstr ""
"PCBA AOI is an intelligent optical inspection system for electronics "
"manufacturing. Built around visual AI, it provides a complete workflow from "
"automatic programming and parameter generation to defect detection and "
"continuous optimization. Unlike traditional approaches that need frequent "
"manual tuning, it adapts quickly to the production floor, improving "
"efficiency while ensuring accuracy and stability. With adaptive algorithms "
"and a feedback mechanism, the software detects both common and subtle "
"defects and keeps learning during production, raising yield and lowering "
"maintenance cost."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:9
msgid "本章节演示如何使用 AOI 系统快速完成一块 PCB 的建模、检测与反馈流程。"
msgstr ""
"This chapter walks through using the AOI system to quickly complete the "
"modeling, inspection, and feedback flow for one PCB."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:17
msgid "启动软件"
msgstr "Launch the Software"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:19
msgid "在开始之前，建议您进行以下设置以优化性能："
msgstr ""
"Before you start, we recommend the following settings to optimize "
"performance:"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:21
msgid ":ref:`如何避免 GPU 进入低功耗模式导致推理变慢？`"
msgstr ":ref:`如何避免 GPU 进入低功耗模式导致推理变慢？`"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:22
msgid ":ref:`如何开启浏览器的硬件加速以避免浏览器卡顿？`"
msgstr ":ref:`如何开启浏览器的硬件加速以避免浏览器卡顿？`"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:24
msgid "在桌面点击启动器即可启动软件。"
msgstr "Click the launcher on the desktop to start the software."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
msgid "启动软件界面"
msgstr "Launcher screen"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:30
msgid ""
"浏览器将自动打开 ``http://localhost:3005/``。 后端默认地址为 ``http://localhost:8000/``。"
msgstr ""
"The browser opens ``http://localhost:3005/`` automatically. The backend "
"defaults to ``http://localhost:8000/``."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
msgid "登录界面"
msgstr "Login screen"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:37
msgid ""
"如需更换后端地址，可在登录页点击 :ui-btn:`Change Host Address（更改主机地址）`，在弹窗中填写后端 URL 后保存。"
msgstr ""
"To change the backend address, on the login page click :ui-btn:`Change Host "
"Address`, enter the backend URL in the dialog, and save."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
msgid "更改主机地址"
msgstr "Change host address"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:44
msgid "如需从其他设备访问，将 ``localhost`` 替换为目标机器的 IP。"
msgstr ""
"To access from another device, replace ``localhost`` with the target "
"machine's IP."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:48
msgid "登录与设置"
msgstr "Login and Settings"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:50
msgid "首次进入可以使用 **管理员** 账号登录：用户名 **admin**，密码在部署时提供。"
msgstr ""
"On first use, log in with the **administrator** account: username **admin**,"
" password provided at deployment."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:52
msgid ""
"登录后，点击右上角的 :ui-btn:`齿轮图标` 进入 :ui-tab:`设置` 页面。设置页左侧分为 :ui-tab:`团队`、:ui-"
"tab:`管理模型`、:ui-tab:`系统设置` 等分组。"
msgstr ""
"After logging in, click the :ui-btn:`gear icon` in the top-right to open the"
" :ui-tab:`Settings` page. The left side of Settings is divided into :ui-"
"tab:`Team`, :ui-tab:`Manage Models`, :ui-tab:`System Settings`, and other "
"groups."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
msgid "设置界面"
msgstr "Settings screen"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:58
msgid ""
"在左侧展开 :ui-tab:`系统设置`，选择 :ui-tab:`语言`，即可在 :ui-param:`系统语言` 中切换界面语言（如 :ui-"
"opt:`English` / :ui-opt:`中文`）。语言设置会保存在系统中，并在系统重启后生效。"
msgstr ""
"Expand :ui-tab:`System Settings` on the left and pick :ui-tab:`Language`; "
"then switch the UI language under :ui-param:`System Language` (e.g. :ui-"
"opt:`English` / :ui-opt:`中文`). The choice is saved and still applies after a"
" system restart."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
msgid "语言设置"
msgstr "Language setting"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:64
msgid "更多设置选项请参见 :ref:`系统管理` 章节。"
msgstr "For more settings, see the :ref:`系统管理` chapter."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:67
msgid "注册产品"
msgstr "Register a Product"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:69
msgid ""
"在主页点击 :ui-btn:`训练PCBA`，注册新的 PCBA/产品，进入 :ui-tab:`自动编程向导`。向导分为 4 "
"个步骤：**基本信息**、**上板与拍摄**、**配置自动编程**、**添加 CAD（可选）**。"
msgstr ""
"On the home page, click :ui-btn:`Teach PCBA` to register a new PCBA/product "
"and enter the :ui-tab:`Programming with Wizard`. The wizard has 4 steps: "
"**Basic Info**, **Conveyor & Capture**, **Configure Auto-Program**, and "
"**Add CAD (Optional)**."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:71
msgid "**1. 基本信息**"
msgstr "**1. Basic Info**"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:73
msgid ""
"输入 :ui-param:`产品名称`，按需添加 :ui-param:`标签`，并填写已知的 PCB :ui-param:`板长度` 与 :ui-"
"param:`板宽度` 等尺寸，单位为 mm，通常来自产品图纸或 SMT 工单；尺寸在产品创建后不可修改。完成后点击 :ui-"
"btn:`下一步`。检测类型、参数与健康检查不在此步设置，已移至第三步 **配置自动编程**。"
msgstr ""
"Enter the :ui-param:`Product Name`, add :ui-param:`Labels` as needed, and "
"fill in the known PCB :ui-param:`board length` and :ui-param:`board width` "
"(in mm, usually from the product drawing or SMT work order; the dimensions "
"cannot be changed after the product is created). Click :ui-btn:`Next` when "
"done. Inspection types, parameters, and health checks are not set on this "
"step — they have moved to Step 3, **Configure Auto-Program**."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
msgid "创建产品-基本信息"
msgstr "Create product — Basic Info"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:79
msgid "**2. 上板与拍摄**"
msgstr "**2. Conveyor & Capture**"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:81
msgid ""
"选择对应传送带并点击 :ui-btn:`锁定`；在线版本中确认或调整传送带宽度；点击 :ui-btn:`进板` 将 PCB 输送至拍摄区域，然后点击 "
":ui-btn:`拍摄2D图像`。系统联动相机与传送带分区采集并自动拼接生成完整 PCB 图像，结果直接显示在本步骤中。请尽量使用洁净、无缺陷的 "
"**Golden board（良品板）**；必要时可调整相机参数（如 :ui-param:`曝光时间`、:ui-param:`增益`、:ui-"
"param:`gamma` 等）后重新拍摄。拼接图像满意后点击 :ui-btn:`下一步`。"
msgstr ""
"Select the conveyor and click :ui-btn:`Lock`; on the online version, confirm"
" or adjust the conveyor width; click :ui-btn:`PCB In` to feed the PCB to the"
" capture area, then click :ui-btn:`Capture 2D Image`. The system acquires "
"the board in tiles with the camera and conveyor and stitches the full PCB "
"image, shown directly on this step. Use a clean, defect-free **Golden "
"board** where possible; if needed, adjust the camera parameters (such as "
":ui-param:`Exposure time`, :ui-param:`Gain`, :ui-param:`gamma`) and re-"
"capture. Click :ui-btn:`Next` once the stitched image looks right."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
msgid "创建产品-上板与拍摄"
msgstr "Create product - Conveyor & Capture"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:87
msgid "**3. 配置自动编程**"
msgstr "**3. Configure Auto-Program**"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:89
msgid ""
"系统显示上一步拼接出的完整图像（只读）。点击 :ui-btn:`定义区域` "
"框选用于自动编程的有效区域（通常为整板；若需排除治具/夹具边缘，可适当收缩）。在 :ui-param:`自动编程检测类型` 中勾选关注的检测项（如 "
":ui-opt:`本体`、:ui-opt:`极性`、:ui-opt:`焊点`、:ui-opt:`焊盘沾胶`、:ui-opt:`IC引脚`、:ui-"
"opt:`文字` 等），并按需在 :ui-param:`自动编程参数` 中调整参数、设置 :ui-param:`健康检查`。若产品为拼板，开启 :ui-"
"opt:`启用拼板` 并填写行 / 列。完成后点击 :ui-btn:`下一步`。"
msgstr ""
"The system shows the full image stitched in the previous step (read-only). "
"Click :ui-btn:`Define Region` to box the effective area for auto-programming"
" (usually the whole board; shrink it to exclude fixture/jig edges). In :ui-"
"param:`AI-modelled inspection types` check the items you care about (such as"
" :ui-opt:`Mount`, :ui-opt:`Polarity`, :ui-opt:`Solder`, :ui-opt:`Glue on "
"Pad`, :ui-opt:`IC Lead`, :ui-opt:`Text`), adjust the corresponding "
"parameters under :ui-param:`Auto Programming Parameters` as needed, and set "
"the :ui-param:`Health check`. If the product is panelized, turn on :ui-"
"opt:`Enable panelization` and fill in rows / columns. Click :ui-btn:`Next` "
"when done."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
msgid "创建产品-配置自动编程"
msgstr "Create product - Configure Auto-Program"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:95
msgid "**4. 添加 CAD（可选）**"
msgstr "**4. Add CAD (Optional)**"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:97
msgid ""
"提供 CAD（``.csv``）文件后，系统可自动读取封装(Package)、丝印/标识、料号(PN)、X/Y "
"坐标与旋转角度，并按封装或料号聚类，使同类元件一次建模、加速训练，同时减少后续人工分组与命名工作。"
msgstr ""
"After providing a CAD (``.csv``) file, the system reads Package, "
"silkscreen/designator, Part No (PN), X/Y coordinates, and rotation, and "
"clusters by package or part number so identical components are modeled once "
"— speeding up training and reducing later manual grouping and naming."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:99
msgid ""
"上传 ``.csv`` 文件后点击 :ui-"
"btn:`预览表格`，在字段映射界面依次指定：料号(PN)、封装(Package)、X、Y、旋转(°)，（可选）层/板面字段；选择坐标单位（mm 或 "
"mil），确认原点与方向一致，随后点击 :ui-btn:`运行自动编程`。若 CAD "
"与拍摄图像未正确重合，可在对齐界面通过旋转、平移、缩放微调后重新运行。"
msgstr ""
"After uploading the ``.csv``, click :ui-btn:`Preview Table` and, in the "
"field-mapping view, assign: Part No (PN), Package, X, Y, Rotation (°), and "
"(optionally) layer/side fields; pick the coordinate unit (mm or mil), "
"confirm the origin and orientation match, then click :ui-btn:`Run Auto "
"Programming`. If the CAD and captured image do not align, adjust by rotate /"
" translate / scale in the alignment view and re-run."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:101
msgid "若不提供 CAD，后续自动编程仍可执行；检测质量不受影响，仅失去基于封装/料号的聚类加速，系统将对元件逐一建模。自动编程耗时约 30 秒。"
msgstr ""
"Without CAD, auto-programming still runs; detection quality is unaffected — "
"you only lose package/part-based clustering, and the system models each "
"component individually. Auto-programming takes about 30 seconds."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
msgid "创建产品-添加 CAD"
msgstr "Create product — Add CAD"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:108
msgid "产品编程页面"
msgstr "Product Programming Page"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:110
msgid "自动编程完成后，会进入 :ui-tab:`产品编程页面`。顶部提供多个标签页："
msgstr ""
"After auto-programming finishes, the :ui-tab:`Product Programming Page` "
"opens. The top offers several tabs:"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:112
msgid ":ui-tab:`标记/对齐 PCB`"
msgstr ":ui-tab:`Mark / Align PCB`"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:113
msgid ":ui-tab:`模板编辑器`"
msgstr ":ui-tab:`Template Editor`"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:114
msgid ":ui-tab:`PCB 拼板`"
msgstr ":ui-tab:`PCB Array`"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:115
msgid ":ui-tab:`整板检测`"
msgstr ":ui-tab:`Whole Board Inspection`"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:117
msgid "左侧还可在 :ui-tab:`设置（Recipe）` 与 :ui-tab:`元件（Component）` 视图之间切换。"
msgstr ""
"On the left you can also switch between the :ui-tab:`Recipe` and :ui-"
"tab:`Component` views."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:119
msgid "**标记/对齐 PCB**："
msgstr "**Mark / Align PCB**:"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:121
msgid ""
"点击 :ui-btn:`+ 标记`，在 PCB 上 **对角位置** 分别框选 2 "
"个固定的参考标记点（圆形、矩形或复杂图案均可）。框选区域应略大，以保证在轻微位移情况下仍能正确定位。当前版本最多支持 2 个 mark 点。如使用 "
"A/B 面双产品检测，可另外点击 :ui-btn:`+ 独特标记` 在每个产品上标记一处差异明显的区域，便于系统自动区分 A/B 面。"
msgstr ""
"Click :ui-btn:`+ Mark` and box two fixed reference marks at **opposite "
"corners** of the PCB (circular, rectangular, or a complex pattern). Make the"
" boxes slightly larger so positioning still works under a small shift. The "
"current version supports at most 2 mark points. For A/B-side mixed-product "
"inspection, also click :ui-btn:`+ Unique Marker` to mark a clearly different"
" area on each product, so the system can tell the A/B sides apart."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
msgid "标记对齐示例"
msgstr "Mark / align example"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:127
msgid "**模板编辑器**："
msgstr "**Template Editor**:"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:129
msgid ""
"左侧显示自动编程获得的元件列表（可在 :ui-opt:`元件` / :ui-opt:`料号` 之间切换）。若上传了 "
"CAD，系统会自动显示丝印/标识并将同类元件分组。可通过搜索栏过滤存在问题的项；对于标记不正确的元件，可手动删除并重新编程。"
msgstr ""
"The left shows the component list from auto-programming (switch between :ui-"
"opt:`Component` / :ui-opt:`Part No`). If CAD was uploaded, the system shows "
"silkscreen/designators and groups identical components. Use the search bar "
"to filter problem items; for incorrectly marked components, delete and re-"
"program manually."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
msgid "模板编辑器示例"
msgstr "Template Editor example"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:135
msgid "有关手动编程的详细步骤与编辑工具用法，请参见 :ref:`手动编程与编辑工具`。"
msgstr ""
"For detailed manual-programming steps and editing tools, see "
":ref:`手动编程与编辑工具`."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:138
msgid "训练和评估"
msgstr "Training and Evaluation"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:140
msgid ""
"确认全部元件框与属性无误后，在 **元件列表** 上方点击 :ui-btn:`训练` 按钮启动模型训练，耗时约 1 分钟；训练完成后再点击 :ui-"
"btn:`自动生成检测参数` 按钮，系统会基于当前模板与训练结果生成一套初始检测参数。需要批量评估所有元件时，点击列表上方的 :ui-"
"btn:`三角形箭头` 即可一键评估。"
msgstr ""
"After confirming all component boxes and attributes, click the :ui-"
"btn:`Train` button above the **component list** to start model training (~1 "
"minute); when done, click :ui-btn:`Generate Detection Params` to generate an"
" initial parameter set from the current template and training results. To "
"evaluate all components at once, click the :ui-btn:`triangle arrow` above "
"the list."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:142
msgid "评估完成后，元件会以颜色标记（绿：健康；红：不健康）。可按需查看不健康项并参考 :ref:`检测参数` 继续微调。"
msgstr ""
"After evaluation, components are color-coded (green: healthy; red: "
"unhealthy). Review unhealthy items as needed and fine-tune per :ref:`检测参数`."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:146
msgid "开始检测"
msgstr "Start Inspection"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:148
msgid "返回主页：点击左上角 Logo 回到主页，点击 :ui-btn:`新建检测任务`。在弹窗中完成任务配置："
msgstr ""
"Back to home: click the logo in the top-left to return home, then click :ui-"
"btn:`New Inspection Task`. Configure the task in the dialog:"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:150
msgid ":ui-param:`传送带`：选择传送带；"
msgstr ":ui-param:`Conveyor`: choose the conveyor;"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:151
msgid ":ui-param:`选择一个 PCBA`：选择已编程的产品；"
msgstr ":ui-param:`Select a PCBA`: pick a programmed product;"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:152
msgid ":ui-param:`选择任务模式`：选择任务模式（如 :ui-opt:`自动连续运行任务`）；"
msgstr ""
":ui-param:`Select Task Mode`: pick a task mode (e.g. :ui-opt:`Auto "
"Continuous Run`);"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:153
msgid ""
":ui-param:`以演示模式运行`：对同一块 PCB 自动连续运行检测，每隔约 5 秒触发一次。适合熟悉复检/反馈流程或现场演示，无需反复手动触发。"
msgstr ""
":ui-param:`Run in Demo Mode`: continuously re-inspects the same PCB, "
"triggering about every 5 seconds. Good for learning the review/feedback flow"
" or for on-site demos, with no repeated manual triggering."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:155
msgid "完成后点击 :ui-btn:`开始检测`。"
msgstr "Click :ui-btn:`Start Inspection` when done."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
msgid "新建检测任务"
msgstr "New inspection task"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:161
msgid "进入 :ui-tab:`检测页面` 后："
msgstr "Once on the :ui-tab:`Inspection Page`:"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:163
msgid "按空格键，或按设备上的 **进板** 实体按键：进板并立即开始检测。更多快捷键请参见 :ref:`快捷键` 章节。"
msgstr ""
"Press the spacebar, or the physical **PCB In** button on the machine: feeds "
"the board and starts inspection immediately. For more shortcuts, see the "
":ref:`快捷键` chapter."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:164
msgid "右侧信息栏：实时显示产品统计（合格/不合格）、元件合格率/不良率/误报率与检测时长（可在整板/子板之间切换）。"
msgstr ""
"Right-hand info panel: shows live product stats (pass/fail), component "
"pass/defect/false-call rates, and inspection time (switchable between whole "
"board and sub-board)."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
msgid "检测页面"
msgstr "Inspection page"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:170
msgid "检测到缺陷的元件会被标记，可查看放大图、定位框、缺陷类型及判定依据，并立即反馈。反馈后的数据会写入数据集，供后续持续优化使用。"
msgstr ""
"Components with detected defects are flagged; you can view the zoomed image,"
" bounding box, defect type, and the basis for the decision, and give "
"feedback immediately. Feedback is written to the dataset for ongoing "
"optimization."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
msgid "复检页面整体视图"
msgstr "Review page overview"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:177
msgid "查看检测历史"
msgstr "View Inspection History"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:179
msgid ""
"在主页点击 :ui-btn:`工作列表` 进入 :ui-tab:`数据分析报告`。页面包含 :ui-tab:`总结`、:ui-"
"tab:`检测结果`、:ui-tab:`不良元件`、:ui-tab:`误判元件` 等标签，并可按 :ui-opt:`今天` / :ui-opt:`昨天`"
" / :ui-opt:`本周` / :ui-opt:`本月` / :ui-opt:`今年` 过滤。"
msgstr ""
"On the home page click :ui-btn:`Work List` to open the :ui-tab:`Data "
"Analysis Report`. The page has tabs such as :ui-tab:`Summary`, :ui-"
"tab:`Inspection Result`, :ui-tab:`Defective Components`, :ui-tab:`False "
"Calls`, and can be filtered by :ui-opt:`Today` / :ui-opt:`Yesterday` / :ui-"
"opt:`This Week` / :ui-opt:`This Month` / :ui-opt:`This Year`."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:181
msgid ":ui-tab:`总结` 提供 OK/NG 数量与比例、告警/误报的 PPM、DPU 等总览指标，以及 NG/OK 比例图。"
msgstr ""
":ui-tab:`Summary` gives overview metrics — OK/NG counts and ratios, "
"alarm/false-call PPM, and DPU — plus an NG/OK ratio chart."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
msgid "数据分析报告-总结"
msgstr "Data Analysis Report — Summary"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:187
msgid ""
"切换到 :ui-tab:`检测结果`，可查看每次检测记录：PCBA 名称、序列号、元件数、不良/告警元件数、检测起止时间等。点击某条记录的 :ui-"
"btn:`查看` 进入复检详情。"
msgstr ""
"Switch to :ui-tab:`Inspection Result` to see each inspection record: PCBA "
"name, serial number, component count, defective/alarm component counts, "
"start/end time, etc. Click :ui-btn:`View` on a record to open the review "
"detail."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
msgid "检测结果列表"
msgstr "Inspection result list"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:193
msgid "在复检详情中，左侧列出不良元件，中部与右侧展示整板及缺陷的放大图、定位框、缺陷类型与判定依据，并可直接反馈。"
msgstr ""
"In the review detail, the left lists defective components, while the center "
"and right show the whole board and zoomed defects with bounding boxes, "
"defect types, and decision basis; you can give feedback directly."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
msgid "复检详情与反馈"
msgstr "Review detail and feedback"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:199
msgid "提交的反馈会写入数据集，用于后续再训练与参数自适应迭代。"
msgstr ""
"Submitted feedback is written to the dataset for later retraining and "
"adaptive parameter iteration."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:203
msgid "迭代模型"
msgstr "Iterate the Model"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:205
msgid "反馈写入数据集后，回到 :ui-tab:`产品编程页面` 重新训练并评估，针对仍为红色的异常元件微调参数即可完成一次迭代。"
msgstr ""
"After feedback is written to the dataset, return to the :ui-tab:`Product "
"Programming Page` to retrain and evaluate; fine-tune parameters for "
"components still marked red to complete one iteration."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:207
msgid ""
"在复检页提交反馈后，也可直接点击 :ui-btn:`AI 更新（AI Update）` 一键据反馈更新检测参数并重训，再点 :ui-"
"btn:`应用参数更新（Apply Param Updates）` 并重新加载会话即可生效，无需回到编程页。"
msgstr ""
"After submitting feedback on the review page, you can also click :ui-btn:`AI"
" Update` to update detection parameters and retrain from the feedback in one"
" click, then click :ui-btn:`Apply Param Updates` and reload the session to "
"apply — no need to go back to the programming page."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:212
msgid "以上即为快速开始全部流程，感谢您的使用。后续更多功能与更详细的说明请继续阅读完整用户手册。"
msgstr ""
"That completes the Quick Start flow. Thank you for using the system. For "
"more features and detail, continue with the full user manual."

